stories.text: I feel like there is more and more posts about existential crisis and anxiety. I don't know if I'm noticing it more because it's resonating with me or are these issues becoming more prominent. I feel like the general sentiment here is atheism and maybe nihilism from people in tech who have more money than they need and now they don't know what to do next. It could be it's just me projecting as well. What I'm asking myself is is it becoming unhealthy for me to come here every day and read about these topics because they could be amplifying my own issues and there isn't really an answer to these questions.
